shows.title: Celebrity Weakest Link
shows.plot_overview: A rapid-fire quiz show in which eight celebrities compete to win up to one million dollars for the charity of their choosing.

shows.title: Fear Factor: The Next Chapter
shows.plot_overview: Strangers must coexist in a harsh, isolated place while facing extreme challenges and playing a devious social game where trust is scarce and fear becomes a strategic tool.

shows.title: Next Level Baker
shows.plot_overview: Talented bakers compete through three challenging rounds, crafting spectacular seasonal treats. Only one will emerge victorious and be crowned the ultimate holiday champion.

shows.title: Stalking Samantha: 13 Years of Terror
shows.plot_overview: Chained in a soundproof box by the man who stalked her for over a decade, Samantha must rely on her mind to survive. As she escapes, she faces a brutal choice: put Christopher behind bars on lesser charges or risk everything in pursuit of justice.

shows.title: Songs & Stories with Kelly Clarkson
shows.plot_overview: The three-time Grammy winner will chat with Gloria Estefan, Jonas Brothers, Lizzo, and Teddy Swims about music as well as their personal lives, giving viewers a “a front-row pass” at their “unfiltered” conversations. The four-episode special will also feature musical performances in an “intimate, unplugged setting.

shows.title: Tinker Bell and the Legend of the NeverBeast
shows.plot_overview: An ancient myth of a massive creature sparks the curiosity of Tinker Bell and her good friend Fawn, an animal fairy who’s not afraid to break the rules to help an animal in need. But this creature is not welcome in Pixie Hollow — and the scout fairies are determined to capture the mysterious beast, who they fear will destroy their home. Fawn must convince her fairy friends to risk everything to rescue the NeverBeast.

shows.title: Justice League: Throne of Atlantis
shows.plot_overview: After the events of Justice League: War, Ocean Master and Black Manta have declared a war against the surface in retaliation of the aftermath of Apokoliptian-tyrant Darkseid's planetary invasion. Queen Atlanna seeks out her other son, Ocean Master’s half-brother Arthur Curry, a half-human with aquatic powers with no knowledge of his Atlantean heritage, to restore balance. shows.title: The Taking of Deborah Logan
shows.plot_overview: What starts as a poignant medical documentary about Deborah Logan's descent into Alzheimer's disease and her daughter's struggles as caregiver degenerates into a maddening portrayal of dementia at its most frightening, as hair-raising events begin to plague the family and crew and an unspeakable malevolence threatens to tear the very fabric of sanity from them all.

shows.title: No King Stands Alone
shows.plot_overview: In the wake of a fallen empire, a fractured alliance faces a rising threat from within. Old betrayals resurface, new forces emerge, and survival demands sacrifice. What began as a case - becomes a war for control.

shows.title: On Brand with Jimmy Fallon
shows.plot_overview: Marketing pros compete in creative challenges, crafting jingles, brand experiences, and ads while working directly with real companies. One winner takes home the title and prize money.

shows.title: Wonder Woman
shows.plot_overview: An Amazon princess comes to the world of Man in the grips of the First World War to confront the forces of evil and bring an end to human conflict.

shows.title: Beta Crystal
shows.plot_overview:
The galaxy is in chaos. Ruled over by the iron fist of the intergalactic warlord known only as Console, all planets quake in fear at his name.

Twins Xandr and Kayi set out to take down Console and free the entire universe from his grasp.

shows.title: Aquaman
shows.plot_overview: Half-human, half-Atlantean Arthur Curry is taken on the journey of his lifetime to discover if he is worth of being a king.
